# Short relative displacement of the base in the CURRENT base frame, executed
# as a direct cmd_vel closed loop on odom TF — bypasses Nav2 and the costmaps
# entirely. For small deliberate sidesteps only (e.g. doing_laundry strafes
# 1 m left after grabbing the basket so the held basket clears the washing
# machine before normal navigation starts). Nothing checks for obstacles along
# the way — keep displacements short and use MoveLocation/GoToPose for real
# navigation.
float32 dx     # forward (+) / backward (-) meters, in the base frame at start
float32 dy     # left (+) / right (-) meters
float32 dyaw   # final heading change (rad, CCW)
---
bool success
string error
